'''羅興亞人種族滅絕'''，指的是[[緬甸国防军|緬甸国防军]]对該國西部[[若開邦|若開邦]][[羅興亞人|羅興亞人]]的迫害。安全部隊在行動中有大規模的[[戰爭罪行|戰爭罪行]]，包括[[就地正法|就地正法]]與[[肢體暴力|肢體暴力]]等。<ref>{{Cite web|date=23 January 2020|title=World Court Rules Against Myanmar on Rohingya|url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2020/01/23/world-court-rules-against-myanmar-rohingya|access-date=3 February 2021|website=Human Rights Watch|language=en}}</ref><ref name=":8">{{Cite web|date=7 December 2017|title=Myanmar's Rohingya Crisis Enters a Dangerous New Phase|url=https://www.crisisgroup.org/asia/south-east-asia/myanmar/292-myanmars-rohingya-crisis-enters-dangerous-new-phase|access-date=3 February 2021|website=Crisis Group|language=en}}</ref>[[聯合國|聯合國]]、[[國際特赦組織|國際特赦組織]]等人權團體、[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]和[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]政府對該行動做了批評，部份人聲稱緬甸軍隊侵犯了人權，並因此批評掌握緬甸政府實權的[[國務資政_(緬甸)|國務資政]][[昂山素季|昂山素季]]，認為她對這個問題不採取行動、沉默、未加阻止。<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-38168917|title=Who will help Myanmar's Rohingya?|date=2017-01-10|newspaper=BBC News|accessdate=2017-02-05|language=en|archive-date=2019-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190413050220/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-38168917|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[中華人民共和國|中國]]<ref name=tg20171224>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/dec/24/china-russia-oppose-un-resolution-myanmar-rohingya-muslims|title=China and Russia oppose UN resolution on Rohingya|first=Agence France-Presse at the United|last=Nations|date=24 December 2017|website=the Guardian|accessdate=3 October 2018|archive-date=2017-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227214347/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/dec/24/china-russia-oppose-un-resolution-myanmar-rohingya-muslims|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[印度|印度]]<ref name=reuters20170814>{{Cite news |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-myanmar-rohingya-india-idUSKCN1AU0UC |title=India says to deport all Rohingya regardless of U.N. registration |publisher=Reuters |date=2017-08-14 |accessdate=2020-02-01 |archive-date=2018-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181207200248/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-myanmar-rohingya-india-idUSKCN1AU0UC |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="bbc41318225">{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-41318225 |title=Are the Rohingya India's 'favourite whipping boy'? |work=BBC News |date=2017-09-25 |language=en |accessdate=2020-02-01 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502232440/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-india-41318225 |dead-url=no }}（[http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41385250 中文報導] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-41385250 |date=20180619103543 }}）</ref>、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]<ref name="oc-media">{{cite web|url=http://oc-media.org/russian-muslims-break-with-kremlin-over-myanmar/|website=oc-media.org|title=oc-media.org/russian-muslims-break-with-kremlin-over-myanmar/|accessdate=14 September 2017|archive-date=2020-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200201133503/https://oc-media.org/russian-muslims-break-with-kremlin-over-myanmar/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[日本|日本]]<ref name="mofa">{{cite web|url=http://www.mofa.go.jp/press/release/press4e_001703.html|website=mofa.go.jp|title=The Attacks in Northern Areas of Rakhine State in Myanmar and the Release of the Final Report by the Advisory Commission on Rakhine State (Statement by Foreign Press Secretary Norio Maruyama) ｜ Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Japan|accessdate=14 September 2017|archive-date=2020-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200227091006/https://www.mofa.go.jp/press/release/press4e_001703.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>等國家支持緬甸政府打擊[[羅興亞人|羅興亞人]]武裝組織。

==背景==
根據緬甸國家報告，2016年10月9日，若開邦的一些武裝人員襲擊了幾個邊界警察營地，造成9名警察死亡，武器和彈藥也被搶走。主要攻擊發生在[[貌奪|貌奪]]鎮。攻擊者的真實身份仍然未知。為了應對這些攻擊，緬甸安全部隊開始對羅興亞穆斯林進行大規模武裝行動。而羅興亞人認為遭到濫殺。<ref name=":0" />
	
==镇压==
在襲擊警察營地事件發生後，緬甸軍隊開始在若開邦北部的村莊執行武裝行動。在最初的行動中，有幾十人死亡許多人被捕。隨著行動繼續，傷亡人數增加。出現了任意逮捕，法外處決，[[輪姦|輪姦]]和對平民的暴行和搶劫。<ref name="Amnesty-Vicious">{{cite web|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/press-releases/2016/12/myanmar-security-forces-target-rohingya-viscious-scorched-earth-campaign/|title=Myanmar: Security Forces Target Rohingya During Vicious Rakhine Scorched-Earth Campaign|date=19 December 2016|publisher=[[Amnesty_International|Amnesty International]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202001842/https://www.amnesty.org/en/press-releases/2016/12/myanmar-security-forces-target-rohingya-viscious-scorched-earth-campaign/|archive-date=2 February 2017|url-status=live|access-date=20 January 2017}}</ref><ref name="Shoot-first">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/15/asia/myanmar-rakhine-state-unrest/|title='Shoot first, ask questions later': Violence intensifies in Rakhine State|author=Joshua Berlinger|date=16 November 2016|publisher=CNN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220145001/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/15/asia/myanmar-rakhine-state-unrest/|archive-date=20 December 2016|url-status=live|access-date=11 December 2016}}</ref><ref name="TI-UN-Kyi">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/burma-rohingya-myanmar-muslims-united-nations-calls-on-suu-kyi-a7465036.html|title=UN calls on Burma's Aung San Suu Kyi to halt 'ethnic cleansing' of Rohingya Muslims|author=Matt Broomfield|date=10 December 2016|newspaper=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|access-date=12 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161211125521/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/burma-rohingya-myanmar-muslims-united-nations-calls-on-suu-kyi-a7465036.html|archive-date=11 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>據媒體報導，到目前為止已有數百名羅興亞人喪生，大約有2萬至3萬名羅興亞人做为难民逃離緬甸，並到[[孟加拉國|孟加拉國]]避難。<ref name="21000-rohingya">{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/21000-rohingya-muslims-flee-bangladesh-escape-persecution-myanmar-1595115|title=21,000 Rohingya Muslims flee to Bangladesh to escape persecution in Myanmar|date=6 December 2016|newspaper=International Business Times|access-date=11 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207154028/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/21000-rohingya-muslims-flee-bangladesh-escape-persecution-myanmar-1595115|archive-date=7 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="ethnic-cleansing">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/nov/24/rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-to-escape-myanmar-military-strikes|title=Myanmar seeking ethnic cleansing, says UN official as Rohingya flee persecution|date=24 November 2016|newspaper=The Guardian|access-date=11 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210021346/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/nov/24/rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-to-escape-myanmar-military-strikes|archive-date=10 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Aljazeera-humanity">{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/12/rohingya-crimes-humanity-amnesty-161219045655733.html|title=Rohingya abuse may be crimes against humanity: Amnesty|date=19 December 2016|newspaper=Al Jazeera|access-date=5 January 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170105160359/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/2016/12/rohingya-crimes-humanity-amnesty-161219045655733.html|archive-date=5 January 2017|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="IBT-1250">{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/new-wave-destruction-sees-1250-houses-destroyed-myanmars-rohingya-villages-1592582|title=New wave of destruction sees 1,250 houses destroyed in Myanmar's Rohingya villages|date=21 November 2016|newspaper=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|access-date=11 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220101309/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/new-wave-destruction-sees-1250-houses-destroyed-myanmars-rohingya-villages-1592582|archive-date=20 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref> <ref name="Lady-CNN">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/17/asia/myanmar-rohingya-aung-san-suu-kyi/|title=Is The Lady listening? Aung San Suu Kyi accused of ignoring Myanmar's Muslims|author=James Griffiths|date=25 November 2016|publisher=CNN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220145049/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/17/asia/myanmar-rohingya-aung-san-suu-kyi/|archive-date=20 December 2016|url-status=live|access-date=11 December 2016}}</ref>

在11月下旬，[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]發布了衛星圖像，顯示大約五條村莊的1,250個羅興亞人房屋被安全部隊燒毀。<ref name="IBT-1250">{{cite news|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/new-wave-destruction-sees-1250-houses-destroyed-myanmars-rohingya-villages-1592582|title=New wave of destruction sees 1,250 houses destroyed in Myanmar's Rohingya villages|date=21 November 2016|newspaper=[[International_Business_Times|International Business Times]]|access-date=11 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220101309/http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/new-wave-destruction-sees-1250-houses-destroyed-myanmars-rohingya-villages-1592582|archive-date=20 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref> <ref name="Shoot-first">{{cite web|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/15/asia/myanmar-rakhine-state-unrest/|title='Shoot first, ask questions later': Violence intensifies in Rakhine State|author=Joshua Berlinger|date=16 November 2016|publisher=CNN|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220145001/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/11/15/asia/myanmar-rakhine-state-unrest/|archive-date=20 December 2016|url-status=live|access-date=11 December 2016}}</ref>在11月的一次事件中，緬甸軍隊使用武裝直升機射擊和殺死平民。<ref name="ethnic-cleansing">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/nov/24/rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-to-escape-myanmar-military-strikes|title=Myanmar seeking ethnic cleansing, says UN official as Rohingya flee persecution|date=24 November 2016|newspaper=The Guardian|access-date=11 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210021346/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/nov/24/rohingya-flee-to-bangladesh-to-escape-myanmar-military-strikes|archive-date=10 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="Amnesty-Vicious">{{cite web|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/press-releases/2016/12/myanmar-security-forces-target-rohingya-viscious-scorched-earth-campaign/|title=Myanmar: Security Forces Target Rohingya During Vicious Rakhine Scorched-Earth Campaign|date=19 December 2016|publisher=[[Amnesty_International|Amnesty International]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202001842/https://www.amnesty.org/en/press-releases/2016/12/myanmar-security-forces-target-rohingya-viscious-scorched-earth-campaign/|archive-date=2 February 2017|url-status=live|access-date=20 January 2017}}</ref>由於緬甸政府禁止外國媒體和人權團體進入該地區，因此，平民傷亡的確切數字仍然未知。若開邦也被西方反對緬甸政府的人稱為“資訊黑洞”。<ref name="Shoot-first" />

那些因迫害而逃離緬甸的羅興亞人報告說，[[緬甸國防軍|緬甸國防軍]]殺害男人強姦婦女、燒毀房子，和把孩子們扔在燃燒的房子裏。<ref name="raped-one">{{cite news|url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/167613-They-raped-us-one-by-one-says-Rohingya-woman-who-fled-Myanmar|title='They raped us one by one', says Rohingya woman who fled Myanmar|date=25 November 2016|newspaper=The News International|access-date=9 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210071207/https://www.thenews.com.pk/latest/167613-They-raped-us-one-by-one-says-Rohingya-woman-who-fled-Myanmar|archive-date=10 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="UN-to-Suu-Kyi">{{cite news|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/world/south-asia/un-calls-suu-kyi-visit-crisis-hit-rakhine-1327606|title=UN calls on Suu Kyi to visit crisis-hit Rakhine|date=9 December 2016|newspaper=The Daily Star|access-date=10 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210142803/http://www.thedailystar.net/world/south-asia/un-calls-suu-kyi-visit-crisis-hit-rakhine-1327606|archive-date=10 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><ref name="NYT-Callous">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/16/world/asia/myanmar-rohingya-violence-united-nations.html|title=Myanmar 'Callous' Toward Anti-Rohingya Violence, U.N. Says|author=Nick Cumming-Bruce|date=16 December 2016|newspaper=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|access-date=1 March 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112002432/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/12/16/world/asia/myanmar-rohingya-violence-united-nations.html|archive-date=12 January 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>在納夫河上運送羅興亞難民的船隻常常被緬甸軍方槍擊。<ref name="Gulf-Times">{{cite news|url=http://www.gulf-times.com/story/521473/Hundreds-of-Rohingya-flee-Yangon-crackdown|title=Hundreds of Rohingya flee Yangon crackdown|date=17 November 2016|newspaper=Gulf Times|access-date=11 December 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161209030256/http://www.gulf-times.com/story/521473/Hundreds-of-Rohingya-flee-Yangon-crackdown|archive-date=9 December 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>2017年1月，至少有四名警察被政府當局拘留，在2016年11月安全部隊打擊羅興亞人穆斯林的影片公開後，政府當局拘留了該名警察。這是自從鎮壓開始以來，政府在該地區懲罰自己的安全部隊的第一起事件。<ref name=":0" />

== 國際反應 ==
{{main|{{le|羅興亞種族滅絕的反應|International reactions to the Rohingya genocide}}}}

緬甸政府對羅興亞人的軍事打擊遭到西方一些國家和人權組織的批評。[[大赦國際|大赦國際]]對羅興亞少數民族的軍事鎮壓稱為“危害人類罪”，並說軍隊將平民作為“有計劃的暴力行為”的目標。12月，聯合國強烈批評緬甸政府對待羅興亞人的態度，稱之「冷酷無情」。緬甸政府的行動也遭到[[孟加拉國|孟加拉國]]、[[馬來西亞|馬來西亞]]和[[印尼|印尼]]的抗議。

緬甸實際上的[[政府首腦|政府首腦]]，[[國務資政|國務資政]]和[[諾貝爾和平獎|諾貝爾和平獎]]獲得者[[昂山素季|昂山素季]]特別受到批評。批評內容不乏她對這個問題的不採取行動和沈默，並且沒有採取太多措施防止軍事濫用。她回答說：“告訴我一個沒有人權問題的國家”。前任[[聯合國秘書長|聯合國秘書長]][[安南|安南]]在若開邦訪問了一星期後，對該地區人權表示深切關注。早些時候，聯合國辦事處說，對羅興亞人的迫害可以被視為危害人類罪。<ref name=":0" />2016年起，[[联合国|联合国]]第七任秘书长[[科菲·安南|科菲·安南]]因此受邀请带领半官方团队针对羅興亞問題进行调查<ref>{{cite web|title=缅甸将邀请联合国前秘书长安南帮助解决若开邦问题|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-08/25/c_1119452786.htm|accessdate=2017-09-07|date=2016-08-25|archive-date=2016-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160908040552/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-08/25/c_1119452786.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再于2017年8月23日刊登若開邦和平宣言，推动措施以改善此地区人民的生活条件。<ref>{{cite web|title=Towards a Peaceful, Fair and Prosperous Future for the People of Rakhine|url=http://www.rakhinecommission.org/the-final-report/|accessdate=2017-09-07|date=2017-08-23|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912064722/http://www.rakhinecommission.org/the-final-report/|dead-url=no}}</ref>缅甸政府于2017年8月24日接受建议书。<ref>{{cite web|title=缅甸赞赏安南等为解决若开邦问题所作努力|url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-08/25/c_1121542545.htm|accessdate=2017-09-07|date=2017-08-25|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825203031/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2017-08/25/c_1121542545.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

根據BBC在2017年9月的報導，因為種種外界較少去了解的歷史恩怨，包含英國殖民時代的仇恨淵源，在[[羅興亞人|羅興亞人]]議題上緬甸民間「幾乎一面倒支持政府，軍方的支持度亦正在增加」，多數民眾所持看法與西方觀點大相逕庭，所以昂山素季政府不論其內心深處真實想法如何都很難去批評，否則無異毀掉自身群眾基礎。<ref name=bbc41344086>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41344086 |title=罗兴亚危机：国际压力下　中国对缅甸的支持有多重要？ |work=BBC中文網 |date=2017-09-21 |accessdate=2017-09-26 |archive-date=2017-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925235908/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/chinese-news-41344086 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

